## 6) Security Escalation Template

When a CRITICAL security finding is discovered:

```
🚨 CRITICAL SECURITY FINDING

Finding: [description]
Location: [file:line]
Severity: CRITICAL

Actions taken:
1. STOPPED all implementation immediately
2. Auto-escalating to MAX mode
3. Will fix security issue BEFORE any other work

Fix plan:
- [concrete steps to fix]

After fix: will re-run full security gate before proceeding.
```

